      = image_tag('andrea_profile.jpg')
    .small-12.medium-6.columns
      %h2 Andrea Deng
      %h3.subheader Summer Coordinator
    .small-12.medium-6.columns.large-text-center.show-for-small-only
      = image_tag('andrea_profile.jpg')
    .small-12.medium-6.columns
      %p
        Andrea is a third-year UC Berkeley undergrad studying Cognitive
        Science with a focus in experience and interaction design. Coming
        from both a technical and user research background, she hopes to
        bridge the gaps between design and development. She is passionate about
        designing products and experiences that build communities and foster
        art, and aim to create an open, creative space where people, passion,
        and ideas mingle.  In her spare time, she loves to learn new things and
        listen to personal stories. She enjoys jamming with friends on the
        guitar and dancing to groovy hip hop.
